18-05-29T21:49:00Z", "attachments": [{"creator": "stransky@redhat.com", "is_obsolete": 1, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8974378}, {"creator": "stransky@redhat.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2018-05-28T17:10:18Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2018-05-15T14:39:50Z", "id": 1756950, "setter": "lsalzman@mozilla.com"}], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8975816}, {"creator": "stransky@redhat.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2018-05-28T17:10:58Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2018-05-15T14:39:50Z", "id": 1756951, "setter": "lsalzman@mozilla.com"}], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8975817}, {"creator": "stransky@redhat.com", "is_obsolete": 1, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8975818}], "votes": 1, "classification": "Components", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "comment_count": 18, "comments": [{"text": "This is a follow up from Bug 788319 comment 47\n\nIn order to make Wayland builds usable, implement run-time GL context switch to use GLX on X11 and EGL on Wayland.", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13265141, "time": "2018-05-09T12:18:19Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8974378\nWIP patch\n\nJeff, what do you think about this approach? It will leave X11/GLX backend as is and we can fix/update EGL for Wayland backend only.", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13265163, "time": "2018-05-09T12:26:11Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8975816\nBug 1460255 - Implement GLContextProviderWayland,\n\nGLContextProviderWayland provides both GLX and EGL GL backends on Wayland enabled builds\nregard an active Gtk+ backend (X11/Wayland).\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244010/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244010/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13278770, "time": "2018-05-15T14:36:09Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8975817\nBug 1460255 - Use GLContextProviderWayland GL provider on Wayland enabled builds,\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244012/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244012/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13278771, "time": "2018-05-15T14:36:09Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8975818\nBug 1460255 - Use gfxXlibSurface::GetGLXPixmap() on GLX only,\n\ngfxXlibSurface::GetGLXPixmap() is provided by GL_PROVIDER_GLX but\nGL_PROVIDER_GLX is not defined by Wayland target.\n\nDon't export gfxXlibSurface::GetGLXPixmap() on Wayland now and leave that\nfor further fixes.\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244014/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244014/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13278772, "time": "2018-05-15T14:36:09Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975816\nBug 1460255 - Implement GLContextProviderWayland,\n\nReview request updated; see interdiff: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244010/diff/1-2/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13278778, "time": "2018-05-15T14:39:50Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975817\nBug 1460255 - Use GLContextProviderWayland GL provider on Wayland enabled builds,\n\nReview request updated; see interdiff: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244012/diff/1-2/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13278779, "time": "2018-05-15T14:39:50Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975818\nBug 1460255 - Use gfxXlibSurface::GetGLXPixmap() on GLX only,\n\nReview request updated; see interdiff: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244014/diff/1-2/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13278780, "time": "2018-05-15T14:39:50Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975816\nBug 1460255 - Implement GLContextProviderWayland,\n\nReview request updated; see interdiff: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244010/diff/2-3/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13368861, "time": "2018-05-28T10:45:04Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975817\nBug 1460255 - Use GLContextProviderWayland GL provider on Wayland enabled builds,\n\nReview request updated; see interdiff: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244012/diff/2-3/", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13368862, "time": "2018-05-28T10:45:04Z"}, {"text": "This is the last missing piece to build Wayland enabled builds on Linux/Gtk.", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13368864, "time": "2018-05-28T10:46:29Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975816\nBug 1460255 - Implement GLContextProviderWayland,\n\nhttps://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244010/#review253364", "author": "lsalzman@mozilla.com", "id": 13369446, "time": "2018-05-28T17:10:18Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8975817\nBug 1460255 - Use GLContextProviderWayland GL provider on Wayland enabled builds,\n\nhttps://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/244012/#review253366", "author": "lsalzman@mozilla.com", "id": 13369447, "time": "2018-05-28T17:10:58Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to Martin Str\u00e1nsk\u00fd [:stransky] from comment #10)\n> This is the last missing piece to build Wayland enabled builds on Linux/Gtk.\n\nsince it's reviewed, can it be pushed?", "author": "david@ixit.cz", "id": 13370406, "time": "2018-05-29T08:14:51Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to David Heidelberg from comment #13)\n> (In reply to Martin Str\u00e1nsk\u00fd [:stransky] from comment #10)\n> > This is the last missing piece to build Wayland enabled builds on Linux/Gtk.\n> \n> since it's reviewed, can it be pushed?\n\nPlease wait until try finishes:\nhttps://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=3f75e43ecb659cbafbeb2332f46eda0085fea971", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13370434, "time": "2018-05-29T08:29:15Z"}, {"text": "*** Bug 1464994 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***", "author": "stransky@redhat.com", "id": 13370854, "time": "2018-05-29T12:23:53Z"}, {"text": "Pus